videos.description: Georgia Tech James Banks III sneaks insides and slams home a dunk from Michael Devoe.
videos.headline: Banks slams home dunk from Devoe

videos.description: James Banks has it stolen away by Garrison Brooks who sends a long pass down court to Seventh Woods who flies in for a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Woods soars for massive dunk

videos.description: Cameron Johnson lets it rip from downtown to start North Carolina off strong in the second half against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Johnson drops deep 3 early in second half

videos.description: Cameron Johnson gets a steal and converts it into a huge dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: Johnson pokes it away and brings it home for huge dunk

videos.description: Nassir Little gets the steal and passes it up to Brandon Robinson who then tosses it behind him placing it perfectly for Little to bring home the dunk.
videos.headline: Robinson throws it behind his head for a Little dunk
